thread.title: Cameron M
thread.title_full: GO Rentals New Zealand reviewed by Cameron M

author: Cameron M
title: Cameron M
text:
Had a great experience from start to finish. Assisted by very friendly staff.
To our surprise we also got a free upgrade which made the trip even better and much more comfortable. We drove over 2400km and it was awesome :D.
tips - although we had an amazing experience with no hassles, always remember to take photos of the car beforehand to prevent any extra unknown charges being dealt to you.
